    * Fixed the RT_io_steps and all related procedures.
      Now it=1 | T=0.      |   file=0
           .   |  .        |   .
          it=n | T=(n-1)*T |  file=(n-1)/RT_io_steps <--> if( (mod(n-1),RT_io_steps)==0 )
           .   |  .        |   .

