4.0.2 (2016-01-14)
------------------

- REPOSITORY reorganization based on decisions taken at the Meeting.
  [Andrea Marini]

  git-svn-id: svn+ssh://qeforge.qe-forge.org/svnroot/yambo-devel/tags/4.0.2@5277 76a4dfbf-5f1f-0410-a543-a0282073b526

